\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Small Signal Model of Figure 3
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset

Consider the following transformation, and then Thevenin equivalent circuit,
 
\begin_inset Float figure
placement H
wide false
sideways false
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\noindent
\align center
\begin_inset ERT
