\begin_inset Formula $L_{1}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{2}$
\end_inset

- together connected in parallel with a capacitor 
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

.
 The oscillatory output is collected from in between the inductor connection.
 
\end_layout

